```

Alternatively, export variables directly in your shell:

```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY="AIza..."
export GEMINI_MODEL="gemini-3.1-flash-lite"
```

## Verify the Setup

```bash
daily-summary doctor
```

A healthy setup looks like:

